  "_doc": "FollowTheMoney.org donor seeds — slug → FTM entity IDs. Used by followthemoney-state-fetch.mjs on --apply. Entity IDs are FTM's internal donor record ids; look one up at https://www.followthemoney.org/show-me?d=<name> and read the URL of the 'detail' link. Multiple entity IDs per slug is normal (corporate PAC + employee donations + subsidiaries are separate FTM records that all roll up to the same TruNorth parent slug). Leave ftm_entity_ids empty for slugs we know are politically active but whose FTM IDs we haven't curated yet — the --apply runner will skip them with a warning, and a follow-up PR can fill them in.",
